### Problem09

```java
public class string{
    public static int len (String x) 
    {
        return __0__;
    }
}
```

Complete static method 'len' so that it takes a string argument, and it returns the length of the string. 

Example:
len("abch")==4

question_content.code:
public class string{
    public static int len (String x) 
    {
        return __0__;
    }
}

